# 可直接替换的 Results 段落

下面这段可用于主文 Results，但需要你们把具体数值替换为已核验的最终表格数值。

```text
We next evaluated whether the advantage of the diffractive frontend persists under object-level distribution shift. To avoid conflating aberration generalization with object memorization, we used two pre-registered evaluation ledgers: one holding out aberration realizations within the training object families, and another holding out object families not used during training. All methods were evaluated with identical seeds, object splits, aberration schedules, and aggregation procedures. The phase-only diffractive frontend achieved the largest mean PSNR gain among the tested methods in the unified comparison, while retaining a positive gain under the held-out object-family protocol. The gain under object-family shift was smaller than that observed for held-out aberrations, indicating that this setting is substantially more challenging. Nevertheless, the positive multi-seed confidence interval suggests that the observed improvement is not solely attributable to memorization of the training object families.
```

中文解释：这段的优点是承认 object-family shift 更难，同时保留核心结论。

