# 可直接替换的 Limitations 段落

```text
This study has several limitations. First, although the phase-only stack provides a physically constrained optical frontend, the present implementation remains a hybrid optical-digital system because reconstruction is performed after intensity detection. We therefore report optical and digital degrees of freedom separately. Second, the gain under held-out object-family shift is smaller than the gain observed for held-out aberrations, indicating that object-level distribution shift remains a challenging regime. Third, although natural-image and hardware-tolerance evaluations improve realism, experimental validation with fabricated diffractive layers remains an important next step.
```

这段必须写。它会降低拒稿风险，因为审稿人看到你们知道边界在哪里。

